OL,3,CChurch needs 'complete reform'
OL,4,Cfollowing Archbishop resignation
OL,6,FThe Dean of Jersey says the Church of
OL,7,FEngland needs a complete reform
OL,8,Ffollowing the resignation of the
OL,9,FArchbishop of Canterbury.
OL,11,FIt comes after the Archbishop, Justin
OL,12,FWelby, faced pressure to step down
OL,13,Ffollowing the publication of The Makin
OL,14,FReview, which detailed his role in
OL,15,Ffailing to act on allegations of child
OL,16,Fabuse.
OL,18,FThere are now calls for an overhaul to
OL,19,Fsave the future of the Church.
