OL,3,CChurch needs 'complete reform'
OL,4,Cfollowing Archbishop resignation
OL,6,FThe Dean of Jersey, the Very Reverend
OL,7,FMike Keirle, said the Makin Report
OL,8,Fmade for "chilling reading".
OL,10,FHe explains: "The details of that
OL,11,Freport (...) I read it with tears
OL,12,Fstreaming down my face when I saw the
OL,13,Fabuse that had taken place in the
OL,14,Fsixties.
OL,16,F"The culture has got to change."
OL,18,FThe Dean of Jersey also says he's
OL,19,Fcommitted to making churches as safe
OL,20,Fas possible.
