OL,3,CChurch needs 'complete reform'
OL,4,Cfollowing Archbishop resignation
OL,6,FThe Archbishop's actions received
OL,7,Fcondemnation from Guernsey as well,
OL,8,Fwith resident and member of the
OL,9,FArchbishops Council Jayne Ozanne
OL,10,Fcalling for significant change within
OL,11,Fthe Church of England.
OL,13,FShe explains: "This needs to be a
OL,14,Fwatershed moment (...) there is a
OL,15,Fwhole institutional problem within it
OL,16,Fabout power, accountability, and its
OL,17,Fcommitment to safeguarding."
